BMaggregator Tracked Addresses
==============================

This is a list of addresses tracked by BMaggregator. To get a daily report of the activity of these addresses subscribe to $mainAddress or see bittext.ch/$bittextMain.

To add a chan to this list send a message from the chan address to $mainAddress with the subject "add chan <ChanName>".

To add your own broadcast address to this list send a message from that address to $mainAddress with the subject "add broadcast <BroadcastLabel>".

For more information about BMaggregator see bittext.ch/bmaggrinfo.


